{"tid":178941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯新型飛彈艇 使用中國製造的發動機","createTime":"2017-03-30T01:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T03:37:33.000Z","uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a26e7c26bd41cf5db5cd2f947bdeb46be915feb","tid":178941,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:31:18.000Z","msg":"使用陸製發動機　俄國導彈艇首次海試就GG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">俄羅斯新型飛彈艇21980型（白嘴鴉雛級）使用中國製造的發動機，於日前的首次海上測試中失敗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。這個發動機是由河南柴油機重工集團製造的TBD620V12，主要優點是油耗低、壽命長和氣動性能好。據河南柴油機重工集團官網資料指出，在用於快艇、巡邏艇上時，該型發動機的輸出功率可達1750千瓦。<br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯《fontanka.ru》報導，21980型在測試中時，柴油發動機發生故障，但報導內容並沒有具體指出什麼原因。綜合外媒報導，俄羅斯一直以來都是由德國MTU公司(MTU為Daimler AG集團旗下公司，是世界級的柴油發動機製造商）供艦用柴油發動機。不過，2014年發生烏克蘭危機後，歐盟對俄羅斯實施經濟制裁，迫使他們轉往中國尋找製造商，並在2015年5月簽訂合約，也一併選擇了的倒順減速器、彈性聯軸器等重要技術零件。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，21980 型飛彈艇由俄羅斯Vympel NPO設計開發，並建造於位在中部雅羅斯拉夫爾（Yaroslavl）地區的雷賓斯克（Rybinsk）造船廠。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯 21980 型飛彈艇是一種噸位120 噸的小型巡邏艇，最高航速23 節，武器裝備有一艇14.5毫米機槍，並有2具反蛙人多管榴彈發射器，以及一座「針刺」防空飛彈發射器。<br />\n<br />\n這座小型肩扛式防空飛彈發射器被稱為飛彈艇，實際上主要任務是港口巡邏、保護水域、打擊沿海水域的破壞恐怖分子，船上配備大口徑機槍、深度收費和便攜式防空導彈系統，而無線電電子設備可以搜索移動的水下目標，潛水系統也可以一次處理多位潛水員。"},{"pid":"bcf5b1f2e5543eae7345fd6493cf7bcc7f290e81","tid":178941,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9cab9887757e25524e6ed2873d3b9ff678228a","tid":178941,"uid":73741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4647f964baea75b3f6d9956c837e3cc555d891d2","tid":178941,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:42:54.000Z","msg":"TBD620V12咪即係德國Deutz AG授權比河柴生產架囉<br />\n俄佬買唔到德國生產都要買德國技術<br />\n可惜支那生產技術垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b1b1f7ef2ffff8d724928c82f0023e99ed3879","tid":178941,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:44:01.000Z","msg":"好波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef7b24ae37c3408bccd8b40bd65d732d85e4913","tid":178941,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:44:35.000Z","msg":"反潛水員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪即係反海豹部隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4aee1a3eeea34c338b719399a89db79a1abb8c0","tid":178941,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T02:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9e6b31b39eb22990f02cfeeba2176b4e6990d6","tid":178941,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:08:25.000Z","msg":"俄佬買錯左潛水系統者。"},{"pid":"25cd1009e4103736920fbb13d7d1ea0570553573","tid":178941,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"陰功豬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾歐盟制裁到迫住用垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9606a7da6d5f2fbf6e24545cddf8732402d855b","tid":178941,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0ce0a7fa7e98b6d2f99ef352b63867b9fef59d","tid":178941,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e4aaab1d18106068963004a1d7dabfefb8128f","tid":178941,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:34:45.000Z","msg":"因為蘇聯年代個引擎廠喺烏克蘭<br />\n而家入侵完人 人地當然唔會賣俾你<br />\n又比歐洲制裁<br />\n<br />\n只好逼住向中國買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12788b2c4a86cac0c00a0fdf899d1bf55ab21bbe","tid":178941,"uid":55045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:37:33.000Z","msg":"入po前心諗用中國製 等壞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}